    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Official release: October 27, 2025</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/ac1b1e6211ff62f958145be8ac88086b.avif?t=1762580521\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras_big/ac1b1e6211ff62f958145be8ac88086b.avif?t=1762580521 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Will you be able to survive the night and unveil the dark secrets lurking within your own home?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">In the middle of the night, when your parents decide to go out and leave you in the care of your older teenage sister, you find yourself embroiled in a new and terrifying adventure. But this time, it will be much more intense than usual. <strong>It could even be the last one</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/057615e8764e3f075d713e21232df9bc.poster.avif?t=1762580521\" width=700 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/057615e8764e3f075d713e21232df9bc.webm?t=1762580521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/057615e8764e3f075d713e21232df9bc.mp4?t=1762580521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/26e7fc4335f882cb6bcc23689ee7fc0f.avif?t=1762580521\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras_big/26e7fc4335f882cb6bcc23689ee7fc0f.avif?t=1762580521 width=800 height=202 /></span>The game's narrative masterfully combines exploration, chilling events, and increasingly complex puzzle-solving. As you explore different areas of your home plunged into <strong>crushing darkness</strong>, you'll gather clues about the former inhabitants and unravel a terrible mystery, including the fate of one of them... <strong>But be careful, the monster is still loose.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/8945441755cc848de3c9108340feeb92.poster.avif?t=1762580521\" width=700 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/8945441755cc848de3c9108340feeb92.webm?t=1762580521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/8945441755cc848de3c9108340feeb92.mp4?t=1762580521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay close attention to every detail and sound; they will be your only guides in the night. Objects and furniture may change places, leaving you trapped and disoriented in your own house. Use the elements you find around you—<strong>they could be your best allies to survive the night and discover that not everything is a product of your imagination.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras/eae9da7fd9722c529b29119307662a3d.avif?t=1762580521\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355440/extras_big/eae9da7fd9722c529b29119307662a3d.avif?t=1762580521 width=800 height=1423 /></span></p>",
